strat.description:
Until the end of the Turning Point, each time a friendly HUNTER CADRE operative (excluding DRONE) is shooting with a pulse weapon, if it hasn’t moved during the activation, or if it’s a counteraction, that weapon has the Ceaseless weapon rule;
if the weapon already has that weapon rule, it has the Relentless weapon rule.
Note this operative isn’t restricted from moving after shooting.

abilities.description:
Each time this operative fights in combat or makes a shooting attack,
if it incapacitates the enemy operative in that combat or shooting attack,
it regains 1D3 lost Wounds.
